Release Information

Netwrix Auditor provides complete visibility of IT
changes and configurations from a single console
Its unified platform enables you to answer who
changed what, when and where for any system or
application in the IT infrastructure - even when
logs are not produced
From Active Directory to SharePoint and everything
in between, you can audit changes to security
configurations, systems and data. With Netwrix
Auditor you will streamline compliance, strengthen
security and simplify root cause analysis
everywhere in your IT environment

Install Notes

1. Unpack & install
2. Use KeyMaker
